The issue this implementation has is that the fold function can properly infer the type of Left and Right at the same time. Look at this usage:

```
const printResult = (result: Either<string, number>) => {
	result.fold(
		(error) => console.log(`Error: ${error}`),
		(value) => console.log(`Result: ${value}`),
