    .map(user => user.age)
    .map(age => age + 1)
    .map(age => `Age next year: ${age}`);
```

### flatMap: Complex Transformations

`flatMap` handles operations that themselves return Try values. This prevents nested Try instances and maintains clean error handling:

```typescript
